text: Erythroxylum kochummenii is a species of plant in the Erythroxylaceae family. It is a tree endemic to Peninsular Malaysia. It is threatened by habitat loss. ==References== kochummenii Category:Endemic flora of Peninsular Malaysia Category:Trees of Peninsular Malaysia Category:Vulnerable flora of Asia Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot
